    slug: 'questions-to-ask-commercial-contractor',
    excerpt:
      'Hiring the wrong contractor can cost you months and thousands of dollars. Here are 15 critical questions every Charlotte business owner should ask before signing a commercial construction contract.',
    date: '2026-04-10',
